mr-auto & ml-auto:

it is like margin-grow,

for mr-auto: the element will take up he remaining space as it's margin-right.

for ml-auto: the element will take up the remaining space as it's margin-left.

* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

LinkContainer: allows us to wrap bootstrap elements like a Link.
                So, if we click on the 'wrapped' element we will go to 
                where to="/address" is directed.